{{Quote|He's&mdash;a borg! Miserable cyborg&hellip; trying to pass!|A [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtrooper]] about [[Beilert Valance/Legends|Beilert Valance]]|<ref name="Star Wars (1977) 29">[[Star Wars (1977) 29|''Star Wars'' (1977) 29]]</ref>}}
"'''Borg'''" was a derogatory abbreviation of "[[Cyborg/Legends|cyborg]]" used by many inhabitants of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], including those residing on [[Aduba-3/Legends|Aduba-3]], in contrast to "normal organics."

